Date: Mon, 30 Oct 2017 13:22:01 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] kuznyechik: implement 128-bit algorithm from GOST R
 34.12-2015

Implement 128-bit algorithm (Kuznyechik) from GOST R 34.12-2015.

Signed-off-by: Dmitry Eremin-Solenikov <dbaryshkov@gmail.com>
